      <title>在Python与R中读取数据和进行描述性统计</title>
      <link href="/2025/02/11/hello-world/"/>
      <url>/2025/02/11/hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在计量经济学中，数据的读取与分析是最基本的功夫。Stata虽然强大，但由于其收费，我们转而依赖R和Python。这两种开源工具能完成几乎所有数据处理工作，且其包与库高效且易用。</p><p>数据从各类格式导入，R和Python都能轻松应对。通过简单的命令，就能把杂乱无章的原始数据转化为可供分析的结构。描述性统计亦然，均值、标准差、分位数等常见统计量可以快速得到，数据的分布、趋势也能通过可视化手段一目了然。在这里，我们用一则从Havarddataverse的真实俄罗斯银行数据（2000-2023）进行演示操作，任何人都可以通过这个链接来下载此数据<a href="https://dataverse.harvard.edu/dataset.xhtml?persistentId=doi:10.7910/DVN/DWUUQJ">data</a>.</p><h2 id="用python读取数据"><a href="#用python读取数据" class="headerlink" title="用python读取数据"></a>用python读取数据</h2><p>我们在这里需要使用pandas与openpyxl包来读取xlsx文件</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="keyword">as</span> pd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> openpyxl</span><br><span class="line">data = pd.read_excel(<span class="string">&quot;financial data of russian banks.xlsx&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(data.head())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结果显示如下</p><table><thead><tr><th>Bank_Name</th><th>Bank_ID</th><th>Year</th><th>…</th><th>Commission expenses</th><th>Net Other Operating Revenues</th><th>Net Profit or Loss</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1БАНК</td><td>1</td><td>2000</td><td>…</td><td>24</td><td>-1862</td><td>2130</td></tr><tr><td>1БАНК</td><td>1</td><td>2001</td><td>…</td><td>27</td><td>-3103</td><td>3155</td></tr><tr><td>1БАНК</td><td>1</td><td>2002</td><td>…</td><td>28</td><td>-3027</td><td>3369</td></tr><tr><td>1БАНК</td><td>1</td><td>2003</td><td>…</td><td>53</td><td>385</td><td>2898</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>（<span class="string">&quot;this is my hose&quot;</span>）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
